    <h2>Continental down? Call today.</h2>
    <p>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura. $120 commercial diagnostic waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410, CSLB C-38 Refrigeration scope. Phones answered 24/7.</p>
